metadata.description: Mr. Green the Grey is a collection of 10,000 MGTG NFTs chillin' on the Ethereum blockchain. Every Greenie is a unique digital collectible as well as your membership in the MGTG Flight Crew and your placeholder in the making of a cartoon movie saga! Welcome to the world of Mr. Green the Grey! More perks, exclusive access, giveaways and members-only activities can be unlocked as we gain access to the the levels of the Athena UFO, hitting our goals together on the roadmap to the Flight Deck! For more details...and to start your abduction... visit www.mrgreenthegrey.com
